  m_text: "<b>Mission Objectives:</b>\n\n- You enter the empty office by the roof.
    No one is working today, but beware to set of any alarm. \n\n- If you trigger
    an alarm you got a few minutes to escape before the police arrives to arrests
    you.\n\n\n<b>Mission Dangers:</b>\n\n- Danger -> Easy\n- People -> None\n- Alarms
    -> Few"
